
Installing on linux (Ubuntu 20.04, debian bullseye)
===================================================

== already installed
== install (with apt-get,  aptitude)
mpv
libmpv-dev
git
python3
    -matplotlib
    -numpy
    -scipy
    -pyqt5
    -pyqt5.qtquick
    -pip
    -yaml
qtdeclarative5-dev
qt5-default
qml-module-qtquick-layout
                  -dialogs
		  -controls
		  -controls2
qml-module-qt-labs-settings
qml-module-qt-labs-folderlistmodel
texlive
texlive-latex-extra

== install with pip3
  pylatex
  python-mpv

  matplotlib moet versie 3.1.3 zijn, dus evt. hier downgraden
  
== the versions should be fairly recent, otherwise there are warnings or errors.
- Basic testing
    - Command:  pdflatex tstlatex.tex
       - yields a pdf file
    - Command:  python tstqtquick.py
       - yields a yellow window
    - Command:  python tstmatplotlib.py
       - a simple plot

== not needed anymore: apply patch for matplotlib with diff_matplotlib
  Change the 3 lines in the file described in the patch-file.
  Without this there are a lot of (harmless) errors on exiting the program.  




